node.text:
Step into Steph's booth as the all-new radio show host for KRCT: Haven's best - and only - radio station. Over four seasons, discover more about Steph's past and her relationships as she makes her mark on the record store, uncovers its secrets – and decides her future.

Life is Strange: True Colors is out September 10, with Steph's DLC, 'Wavelengths', available September 30 on PlayStation, Xbox, PC, and Stadia, and coming to Nintendo Switch later this year.

Pre-order now through the link in our bio!

node.title: Life is Strange: True Colors - Steph 'Wavelengths' DLC Official Trailer

node.text:
Contest alert! Our latest instalment, #LifeisStrange #TrueColors launches on the 10th September and to celebrate, we are giving you the chance to WIN the 𝘂𝗹𝘁𝗶𝗺𝗮𝘁𝗲 𝗽𝗿𝗶𝘇𝗲 𝗯𝘂𝗻𝗱𝗹𝗲!
 
We are excited to share that the game is all about finding yourself and being proud of your individuality. Alex, the main character in True Colors, uses patches on her jacket to express who she is. We're inviting you to 𝗱𝗲𝘀𝗶𝗴𝗻 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗼𝘄𝗻 𝗽𝗮𝘁𝗰𝗵𝗲𝘀 reflecting your personality and to share the story behind your design with us. The winning entry will have their patch produced and sewn onto a custom made jacket, alongside @mxmtoon's designs. (More information on how to get your hands on this jacket to come.🤫)

Not only will the 𝗪𝗜𝗡𝗡𝗘𝗥 have their patch sewn onto the jacket. They will also receive a Nacon x Life is Strange gaming headset, a copy of the Life is Strange: True Colors Ultimate Edition, a Square Enix gift voucher for the Square Enix European or North American online store, and an mxmtoon ukulele.
𝘅𝟯 𝗥𝗨𝗡𝗡𝗘𝗥𝗦 𝗨𝗣 also receive a copy of the Life is Strange: True Colors Ultimate Edition
For full details of all the prizes, check out the full terms and conditions!

TO ENTER OUR CONTEST ⬇️
1. Design your patch for the jacket. Don’t worry if you aren’t the best artist, we are looking for ideas and what the design means to you. We’ll be selecting one (1) grand-prize winner and three (3) runner-up prize winners based on the creativity of the Design and how well the Design supports, communicates, and reflects the story behind it.
2. Upload your entry to your Instagram feed. You must include the inspiration and story behind your designs in the caption, as well as #ShowYourTrueColors and #Contest
3. You must be following @lifeisstrangegame on Instagram, and continue to follow @lifeisstrangegame until the winner is announced. Your account must be public for us to be able to view your entry.
4. The contest ends on September 14, 2021 at 10:00 a.m. Pacific. The contest has no affiliation to Instagram. The contest is open to legal residents of the fifty (50) states of the United States of America, the District of Columbia, and Puerto Rico; Cana
